Package net.sourceforge.gxl

Interface Summary
GXLDocumentListener The listener interface for receiving GXL document modification events.
GXLLocalConnectionTentacle Non-GXL entity representing a tentacle between a GXLLocalConnection and a GXLGraphElement.
 

Class Summary
GXL Provides static GXL constants that can be used if wanted.
GXLAtomicValue Superclass of all atomic values.
GXLAttr Represents the GXL attr element.
GXLAttributedElement Superclass for all GXLElements that can be attributed using attr elements.
GXLAttributeModificationEvent The event that is passed to GXLDocumentListeners when an attribute has been modified.
GXLAttrValueModificationEvent The event that is passed to GXLDocumentListeners when an attr elements value has been replaced.
GXLBag Represents the GXL bag element.
GXLBool Represents the GXL bool element.
GXLCompositeValue Superclass for all composite value elements (that is bag, set, seq and tup).
GXLDocument Represents a GXL document responsible for reading and writing GXL files.
GXLDocumentAdapter Adapter for the GXLDocumentListener interface, providing empty method bodies.
GXLEdge Represents the GXL edge element.
GXLElement Superclass of all GXL elements.
GXLEnum Represents the GXL enum element.
GXLFloat Represents the GXL float element.
GXLGraph Represents the GXL graph element.
GXLGraphElement Superclass for all GXLElements that can be connected by GXLLocalConnections.
GXLGXL Represents the GXL gxl element.
GXLIDGenerator A simple id generator.
GXLInt Represents the GXL int element.
GXLLocalConnection Superclass for GXLEdge and GXLRel providing basic edge functionality.
GXLLocator Represents the GXL locator element.
GXLNode Represents the GXL node element.
GXLRel Represents the GXL rel element.
GXLRelend Represents the GXL relend element.
GXLSeq Represents the GXL seq element.
GXLSet Represents the GXL set element.
GXLString Represents the GXL string element.
GXLTreeModificationEvent The event that is passed to GXLDocumentListeners when an element has been inserted or removed.
GXLTup Represents the GXL tup element.
GXLType Represents the GXL type element.
GXLTypedElement Superclass for all GXLElements that can be typed using the type element.
GXLValue Superclass for all values.
GXLValueModificationEvent The event that is passed to GXLDocumentListeners when a GXLAtomicValue has been modified.
 

Exception Summary
GXLValidationException Thrown when an operation that would render a GXLDocument invalid has been attempted.
